{
  "id": "RAW_14b0b0",
  "title": "12 个被低估的 CSS 特性，让前端开发效率翻倍！",
  "url": "https://juejin.cn/post/7548643374820769801",
  "date": "2025-09-11 06:29:23",
  "author": "前端Hardy",
  "siteName": "掘金本周最热",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body result\">\n   <p>在前端开发的日常中，我们常常围绕着常见的 CSS 属性打转，却忽略了那些藏在规范角落里的<strong>小众特性</strong>。它们看似不起眼，却能在关键时刻简化代码、提升交互质感，成为提升开发效率的秘密武器。今天，就为大家盘点 12 个被严重低估的 CSS 特性，帮你解锁更优雅的开发方式！</p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-0\">1. accent-color：一键美化表单元素</h3>\n   <p>原生复选框、单选按钮的默认样式呆板又难改，曾是很多开发者的 “审美痛点”。而 accent-color 的出现，彻底解决了这个问题 —— 只需一行代码，就能将表单元素的核心颜色替换成品牌色，无需依赖 JavaScript 或第三方组件。</p>\n   <p><strong>兼容性：</strong> Chrome 86+、Firefox 75+、Safari 14+，主流浏览器均支持，可放心使用。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 美化复选框 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[type=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"checkbox\"</span>]</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  accent-<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ff4488</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 品牌粉色 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 美化单选按钮 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[type=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"radio\"</span>]</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  accent-<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#2196f3</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 品牌蓝色 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">input</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"checkbox\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">input</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"radio\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/531e58ea92a2405daacd1db2b944e066~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=gIn9MFnF162bJlf5v9YQq0hViqs%3D\" alt=\"表单元素\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-1\">2. caret-color：定制光标颜色</h3>\n   <p>在深色主题界面中，默认的黑色光标会显得格外刺眼，破坏整体视觉和谐。caret-color 允许我们精准控制输入框光标的颜色，让细节也能贴合设计风格，提升用户输入时的视觉舒适度。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.container</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#1a1a1a</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ffffff</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">caret-color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#F43507</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">input</span>  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ec56acfc2a2649fb95012edf6d1e9b65~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=ZRTi3ZaITyxEAcxYueTNoN4kRqU%3D\" alt=\"定制光标颜色\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-2\">3. currentColor：颜色继承</h3>\n   <p>还在为重复写颜色值而烦恼？currentColor 堪称 CSS 中的 “颜色复印机”—— 它会自动继承元素的 color 属性值，让边框、背景等样式与文字颜色同步，完美遵循 “DRY（Don't Repeat Yourself）” 原则，后续修改颜色时也只需改一处。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.container</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">button</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#0066cc</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 主色调 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> solid currentColor; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 边框继承文字颜色 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: transparent;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* hover时同步变色 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.container</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">button</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:hover</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#f99</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 加深主色调 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 边框会自动变成 #f99，无需重复定义 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span>颜色继承按钮<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/f5760061e71f4cdfb679ccd414bc85f5~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=17Nd8tN1gQFuIvmMKRfz7fQlZFs%3D\" alt=\"颜色继承\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-3\">4. ::marker：轻松定制列表符号</h3>\n   <p>过去修改列表（ul/ol）的符号，要么用 background-image 做 “hack”，要么手动嵌套标签，代码又丑又难维护。而::marker 伪元素让我们能直接控制列表符号的样式，颜色、尺寸、字体都能自定义。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 定制有序列表符号 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">ol</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">li</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::marker</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#e91e63</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 粉色符号 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1rem</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 放大符号 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-weight</span>: bold;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 定制无序列表符号（部分浏览器支持） */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">ul</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">li</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::marker</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">content</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"✨\"</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 用 emoji 当符号 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">  }</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span>我是有序列表1<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span>我是有序列表2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span>我是无序列表1<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span>我是无序列表2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/b3c3eb99322d4aa8be18ab58fb2c9967~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=Z%2F3%2BZiuJOo9kb%2FwncRWbpKd%2FA8M%3D\" alt=\"列表符号\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-4\">5. :user-valid/:user-invalid：更友好的表单验证</h3>\n   <p>传统的:valid/:invalid 伪类会在页面加载时就触发验证反馈（比如空输入框直接显示红色边框），容易打扰用户。而:user-valid 和:user-invalid 只会在用户与表单交互后（比如输入内容、点击提交）才触发样式，既及时提示错误，又不会过度干扰。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 基础样式 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> solid <span class=\"hljs-number\">#bbb</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transition</span>: border-color .<span class=\"hljs-number\">2s</span>, box-shadow .<span class=\"hljs-number\">2s</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 合法 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span>:user-valid {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#4caf50</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-shadow</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">76</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">175</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>, .<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 非法 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:user-invalid</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#f44336</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-shadow</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2px</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">244</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">67</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">54</span>, .<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">input</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">required</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"[A-Za-z0-9]{5,10}\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"5-10位字母数字\"</span>/&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/16c1efb2a4e444d890383704b2c21175~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=EMBvTMenHy0KYDlYKWsJ5qdt%2BvA%3D\" alt=\"表单验证\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-5\">6. :placeholder-shown：捕捉输入框 “空状态”</h3>\n   <p>想在用户输入前给表单加动态效果？:placeholder-shown 伪类可以精准识别输入框是否显示占位符（即用户未输入内容），轻松实现 “空状态提示”“输入时淡入淡出” 等交互。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">36px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">12px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> solid <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ccc</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-sizing</span>: border-box;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 1. 空值时占位符半透明 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:placeholder-shown</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">opacity</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 2. 空值时显示提示图标 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tip-icon</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: none;<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 默认隐藏 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">position</span>: absolute;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">right</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">50%</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">translateY</span>(-<span class=\"hljs-number\">50%</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"24\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">url</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\\&lt;svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"%23999\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"&gt;\\&lt;path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z\"/&gt;\\&lt;/svg&gt;'</span>) no-repeat center/contain;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"25\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"26\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:placeholder-shown</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tip-icon</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"27\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: inline-block; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 空值时显示 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"28\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"field\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">input</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"请输入用户名\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"user\"</span>/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"tip-icon\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">title</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"请输入内容\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"field\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">input</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"搜索关键词\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"search\"</span>/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"tip-icon\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">title</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"请输入搜索内容\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8b96619988bb45a0a6be4dca526debc3~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=OiPRMdfqBf%2FZfGZyMvtNjMeyEw8%3D\" alt=\"输入框空状态\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-6\">7. all: unset：一键清除默认样式</h3>\n   <p>重置组件默认样式时，传统的 reset.css 往往要写几百行代码，冗余又难维护。all: unset 只需一行，就能彻底移除元素的所有默认样式（包括继承属性），相当于给组件 “清空画布”，再按需添加自定义样式。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.custom-btn</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">all</span>: unset; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 清除默认的边框、背景、字体等 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ff9800</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: white;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">cursor</span>: pointer;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span>默认按钮<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"custom-btn\"</span>&gt;</span>unset 按钮<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/a554a760854e4d41bee58a3826941b9a~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=76lcUc%2Fnp908dO6AHpc61eneDEA%3D\" alt=\"清除默认样式\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-7\">8. inset：简化定位布局</h3>\n   <p>写绝对定位（position: absolute）或固定定位（position: fixed）时，常常要重复写 top/right/bottom/left 四行代码。inset 是这四个属性的简写，语法和 padding 类似，能大幅精简代码。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 全屏覆盖（等价于 top:0; right:0; bottom:0; left:0） */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.modal-overlay</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">position</span>: fixed;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  inset: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 上下10px，左右20px（等价于 top:10px; right:20px; bottom:10px; left:20px） */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.card</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">position</span>: absolute;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">  inset: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-8\">9. text-wrap: balance：智能均衡文本折行</h3>\n   <p>在响应式设计中，标题或长文本的折行常常参差不齐（比如一行只有 1-2 个字符），影响排版美感。text-wrap: balance 会自动计算文本长度，让每行的字符数尽量均衡，就像专业排版师调整的效果。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 让标题折行更优雅 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">h2</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  text-wrap: balance;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">max-width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">600px</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 配合最大宽度使用，效果更佳 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>在响应式设计中，标题或长文本的折行常常参差不齐（比如一行只有 1-2 个字符），影响排版美感。text-wrap: balance会自动计算文本长度，让每行的字符数尽量均衡，就像专业排版师调整的效果。<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/0d26e8c5492c45efa7aa0d0d8bd8cb87~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=DKEK8Y8Qn4U%2BjKwKW8vHb8hdYmE%3D\" alt=\"智能均衡文本折行\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-9\">10. :is ()：简化多选择器重复写法</h3>\n   <p>当多个选择器需要应用相同样式时，:is()伪类能减少代码重复，让选择器更简洁。比如给header、main、footer中的p标签设置相同样式：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 传统写法 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">header</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">p</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">main</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">p</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">footer</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">p</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">line-height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.6</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* :is() 简化写法 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:is</span>(<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">header</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">main</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">footer</span>) <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">p</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">line-height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.6</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-10\">11. aspect-ratio：固定元素宽高比</h3>\n   <p>过去实现固定宽高比（比如 16:9 的视频、1:1 的头像），需要用 padding-top 的 “hack” 方法，计算繁琐。aspect-ratio直接定义宽高比，简单直观。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 16:9 视频容器 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.video-container</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  aspect-ratio: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16</span>/<span class=\"hljs-number\">9</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 1:1 头像容器 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.avatar</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">80px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">  aspect-ratio: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">50%</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">overflow</span>: hidden;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin-top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">img</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>; <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>; <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">object-fit</span>: cover; }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\"></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"video-container\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"avatar\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">img</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"https://picsum.photos/200/200\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">alt</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"头像\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/bb2d88ac703f4d4ba5087298fd602516~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=ZeFMD7I1iAM1NQXrZZ4alETsTKE%3D\" alt=\"固定元素宽高比\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-11\">12. scroll-snap-type：实现平滑滚动吸附</h3>\n   <p>做轮播图、步骤导航时，想让滚动到指定位置后自动 “吸附”？scroll-snap-type无需 JavaScript，纯 CSS 就能实现平滑的滚动吸附效果。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 横向滚动容器 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.scroll-container</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">overflow-x</span>: auto;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">scroll-snap-type</span>: x mandatory;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#f5f5f5</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 滚动项 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.scroll-item</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">300px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">200px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">scroll-snap-align</span>: start;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ff9800</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: grid;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">  place-items: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">48px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scroll-container\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scroll-item\"</span>&gt;</span>1<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scroll-item\"</span>&gt;</span>2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scroll-item\"</span>&gt;</span>3<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scroll-item\"</span>&gt;</span>4<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/0bb6315661f144c28d89c264ed42cc6c~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uvSGFyZHk=:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1758176963&amp;x-signature=D93Mw5AUq6NAEiXmFIdQRUzxKBI%3D\" alt=\"实现平滑滚动吸附\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>这 12 个 CSS 特性看似<strong>小众</strong>，却覆盖了表单美化、样式复用、布局简化、交互优化等核心场景 —— 从 1 行代码美化表单，到纯 CSS 实现滚动吸附，每一个都能解决实际开发中的痛点，减少代码量、提升效率。</p>\n   <hr>\n   <p><em>各位互联网搭子，要是这篇文章成功引起了你的注意，别犹豫，<strong>关注、点赞、评论、分享走一波</strong>，让我们把这份默契延续下去，一起在知识的海洋里乘风破浪！</em></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章盘点了 12 个被低估的 CSS 特性，通过代码示例和应用场景，帮助前端开发者提升效率、优化用户体验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章盘点了 12 个被低估的 CSS 特性，通过代码示例和应用场景，帮助前端开发者提升效率、优化用户体验。",
  "summary": "这篇文章为前端开发者深入介绍了 12 个在日常开发中可能被忽略但极具实用价值的 CSS 特性。作者详细阐述了每个特性的功能、使用方法和实际应用场景，并辅以代码示例和效果图。这些特性涵盖了表单美化（如 `accent-color`、`caret-color`）、样式复用（`currentColor`）、列表定制（`::marker`）、空状态捕捉（`:placeholder-shown`）、表单验证（`:user-valid/:user-invalid`）、样式重置（`all: unset`）、布局简化（`inset`）、文本排版（`text-wrap: balance`）、选择器优化（`:is()`）、宽高比固定（`aspect-ratio`）以及滚动吸附（`scroll-snap-type`）。文章旨在帮助开发者利用这些“小众”但高效的 CSS 属性，简化代码、提升开发效率和用户体验，减少对 JavaScript 的依赖。",
